name: Nugget
description: On Pi Day 3/14/22 our gecko Nugget passed away. He was an "Enigma" gecko; it's a neurological condition in geckos, and despite this he lived a long and happy life in a living big home. He loved mealworms and talking to his imaginary friends. You'll be missed, little guy. He'll be buried with 3 dead mealworms in a salted box. One mealworms for everyone who cherished him deeply.
